lor=\"#808080\">&rarr; like V, mA, Hz, ...</font><br />format  <font color=\"#808080\">&rarr; like %d, %03d,... used to convert the integer into a string</font><br />command  <font color=\"#808080\">&rarr; Command format with one \'%s\' ex: &quot;CLOS (@%s)&quot; used in global SCPI command ROUT:CLOS ()</font><br /><br /><strong>REAL</strong></p><p><img src=\"../images/custom/xml_img/xml_real.jpg\" alt=\"XML REAL\" width=\"192\" height=\"82\" /></p><p>mini &nbsp;<font color=\"#808080\">&rarr; minimal value accepted</font><br />maxi  <font color=\"#808080\">&rarr; maximal value accepted</font><br />default  <font color=\"#808080\">&rarr; default value setting</font><br />unit  <font color=\"#808080\">&rarr; like V, mA, Hz</font><br />format  <font color=\"#808080\">&rarr; like %f, %3.1f,... used to convert the real value into a string</font><br />command  <font color=\"#808080\">&rarr; Command format with one \'%s\' ex: &quot;GAIN %s&quot; used in global SCPI command SCAL:GAIN</font> <br /><br /><strong>BOOL</strong></p><p><img src=\"../images/custom/xml_img/xml_bool.jpg\" alt=\"XML BOOL\" width=\"192\" height=\"80\" /></p><p>command &nbsp;<font color=\"#808080\">&rarr; command format with one \'%s\' ex: &quot;:AUTO %s&quot; used in global SCPI command RANGE:AUTO {OFF|ON}</font><br />label_true  <font color=\"#808080\">&rarr; true label displayed like: Auto = ON</font><br />command_true  <font color=\"#808080\">&rarr; string used for the true selection like: ON</font><br />label_false  <font color=\"#808080\">&rarr; false label displayed like: Auto = OFF</font><br />command_false <font color=\"#808080\">&rarr; string used for the false selection like: OFF</font><br /><br /><strong>STRING</strong></p><p><img src=\"../images/custom/xml_img/xml_string.jpg\" alt=\"XML STRING\" width=\"195\" height=\"80\" /></p><p>default &nbsp;<font color=\"#808080\">&rarr; default value setting</font><br />command  <font color=\"#808080\">&rarr; Command format with one \'%s\' ex: &quot;