(25, 6, 'SCPI commands for the ASCII plug-in (Stamp3PlugInASCII.vi)', 5, '2010-08-17 16:04:20', '<p><strong><u>SCPI commands for the ASCII plug-in (Stamp3PlugInASCII.vi</u></strong>)</p><p><em><font color=\"#808080\"><u>Preliminary remark :</u> all the SCPI explanation examples are build with a &quot;COMx&quot; port name, where x stands for the serial port number. </font></em></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;<u><strong>1. Plug-in setting : </strong></u></p><blockquote><p><em><u>1.1. Initialization :</u></em></p><blockquote><p>Command : <font color=\"#800000\">COMx:</font><font color=\"#0000ff\">9600,8,1,0</font></p></blockquote></blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><p>Explanation :&nbsp; </p></blockquote></blockquote><p><strong><u>Init the plug-in</u></strong><br /><font color=\"#800000\">ASRL1::INSTR</font>(<font color=\"#0000ff\">1,19200,2500</font>)<br /><font color=\"#800000\">ASRL1::INSTR</font>  <font color=\"#808080\">&rarr; VISA label</font><br /><font color=\"#0000ff\">1</font> <font color=\"#808080\">&rarr; Slave address</font><br /><font color=\"#0000ff\">19200</font>  <font color=\"#808080\">&rarr; Baud-rate</font><br /><font color=\"#0000ff\">2500</font>  <font color=\"#808080\">&rarr; Timeout</font><br /><br /><strong><u>Reset all coils</u></strong><br /><font color=\"#800000\">OPEN:</font><font color=\"#0000ff\">ALL</font><br /><font color=\"#800000\">OPEN:</font>  <font color=\"#808080\">&rarr; Command</font><br /><font color=\"#0000ff\">ALL</font>  <font color=\"#808080\">&rarr; all the 256 coils <em>(from 0 to 255)</em></font><br /><br /><strong><u>Set coils <em>(Dynamic controls)</em></u></strong><br /><font color=\"#800000\">DOUT:</font><font color=\"#0000ff\">C=0,2</font>|<font color=\"#008000\">O=1,4,6,8</font>|<font color=\"#ff00ff\">D=1.0</font>|<font color=\"#0000ff\">C=1,4,6,8</font>|<font color=\"#008000\">O=0,2</font><br /><font color=\"#800000\">DOUT:</font>  <font color=\"#808080\">&rarr; Command</font><br /><em><font color=\"#993300\">The acti