(95, 11, 'Generic variables list and usage', 4, '2010-09-02 17:45:09', '<p><font size=\"4\"><strong><u>Generic variables available</u></strong></font></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>This generic variables can be used into the test specification to facilitate the description</p><p><strong>Note:</strong></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>To use this generic variables in place of value, write the label into two \'<strong><font color=\"#ff0000\"><font size=\"3\">~</font></font></strong>\' char like this : <strong><font color=\"#ff0000\"><font size=\"3\">~</font></font></strong><strong><font color=\"#3366ff\">SCAN_SERIAL SKU</font></strong><strong><font color=\"#ff0000\"><font size=\"3\">~</font></font></strong>&nbsp;</p><p><strong>Examples:</strong></p><p>&nbsp;</p><blockquote>&nbsp;<u>Display an GUI pop-up with the bitmap name automatically set in accordance with the UUT</u>&nbsp;</blockquote><p>&nbsp;</p><blockquote><font size=\"2\">DIV:USER:GUI:VALID(Product &rsquo;<strong><font color=\"#ff0000\">~SCAN_REF~</font></strong>&rsquo; connexion,Raccordement du produit &rsquo;<strong><font color=\"#ff0000\">~SCAN_REF~</font></strong>&rsquo;,Title xx,S:\\Network Power Solution\\Bitmaps\\UnitHypotFunctionalTest\\Connexion\\<font color=\"#ff0000\"><strong>~SCAN_REF~</strong></font>.jpg)&nbsp;</font></blockquote><p>&nbsp;</p><blockquote>&nbsp;<u>Set automatically the Hipot QuadCheck instrument with the setting need for the UUT</u> &nbsp;</blockquote><blockquote>MEAS:(FFFSSY <strong><font color=\"#ff0000\">~GND_AMPS~</font></strong>S0 <strong><font color=\"#ff0000\">~GND_OHMS~</font></strong>S1 0S2 <font color=\"#ff0000\"><strong>~GND_TIME~</strong></font>S3 4S4 25.0FA) ~(%)~</blockquote><p>&nbsp;</p><p><strong>Variables list:</strong></p><p><font color=\"#3366ff\">TEST_MODE </font><font color=\"#808080\">&rarr; Test mode </font><em><font color=\"#808080\">(FAC&rarr;Factory, RMA &amp; CMA)</font></em></p><p><font color=\"#3366ff\">SCAN_REF </font><font color=\"#808080\">&rarr; SKU Reference</font><br /><font color=\"#3366ff\">SCAN_SERIAL </font><font color=\"#808080\">&rarr; SKU Serial number</font><br /><font color=\"#3366ff\">TEST_START</font> <font color=\"#808080\">&rarr; Test start time stamp</font></p><p><font color=\"#3366ff\">GAME_NAME</font> <font color=\"#808080\">&rarr; Game name <em>(used for path)</em></font><br /><font color=\"#3366ff\">CONTROL_NAME</font> <font color=\"#808080\">&rarr; Control name <em>(used for path)</em></font></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><u>Product Parameters</u><br /><font color=\"#3366ff\">UUT_TOPO</font> <font color=\"#808080\">&rarr; Topology</font><br /><font color=\"#3366ff\">UUT_DESIGN</font> <font color=\"#808080\">&rarr; Designation</font><br /><br /><font color=\"#3366ff\">UUT_POWER</font> <font color=\"#808080\">&rarr; Power <em>(VA)</em></font><br /><font color=\"#3366ff\">UUT_BACKUP</font> <font color=\"#808080\">&rarr; Backup time <em>(mn)</em></font><br /><font color=\"#3366ff\">UUT_VOLT</font> <font color=\"#808080\">&rarr; Voltage <em>(V)</em></font><br /><font color=\"#3366ff\">UUT_FREQ</font> <font color=\"#808080\">&rarr; Frequency <em>(HZ)</em></font><br /><br /><font color=\"#3366ff\">UUT_MODEL</font> <font color=\"#808080\">&rarr; Reference product</font><br /><font color=\"#3366ff\">UUT_PNP</font> <font color=\"#808080\">&rarr; Plug &amp; Play information</font><br /><font color=\"#3366ff\">UUT_FIRM</font> <font color=\"#808080\">&rarr; Firmware rev</font><br /><font color=\"#3366ff\">UUT_SKU		SKU</font> <font color=\"#808080\">&rarr; info</font></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><u>Normative controls parameters</u><br /><em><u>Power:</u></em><br /><font color=\"#3366ff\">HI_VOLT</font> <font color=\"#808080\">&rarr; Tension <em>(V)</em></font><br /><font color=\"#3366ff\">HI_AMPS</font> <font color=\"#808080\">&rarr; Limitation <em>(mA)</em></font><br /><font color=\"#3366ff\">HI_TIME</font> <font color=\"#808080\">&rarr; Maintains (S</font>)<br /><font color=\"#3366ff\">HI_RAMP</font> <font color=\"#808080\">&rarr; Rise <em>(S)<