em></font><br /><font color=\"#3366ff\">MAIN1_IMAX</font> <font color=\"#808080\">&rarr; I maxi <em>(A)</em></font><br /><font color=\"#3366ff\">MAIN1_YIELD</font> <font color=\"#808080\">&rarr; Rendement <em>(&eta;)</em></font><br /><font color=\"#3366ff\">MAIN1_THDI THDI</font> <font color=\"#808080\">&rarr; THID <em>(%)</em></font></p><p><em><u>Main 2:</u></em><br /><font color=\"#3366ff\">MAIN2_U</font> <font color=\"#808080\">&rarr; Tension <em>(V)</em></font><br /><font color=\"#3366ff\">MAIN2_UMAX</font> <font color=\"#808080\">&rarr; U maxi <em>(V)</em></font><br /><font color=\"#3366ff\">MAIN2_UMIN</font> <font color=\"#808080\">&rarr; U mini <em>(V)</em></font><br /><font color=\"#3366ff\">MAIN2_IMAX</font> <font color=\"#808080\">&rarr; I maxi <em>(A)</em></font><br /><font color=\"#3366ff\">MAIN2_YIELD</font> <font color=\"#808080\">&rarr; Rendement <em>(&eta;)</em></font><br /><font color=\"#3366ff\">MAIN2_THDI</font> <font color=\"#808080\">&rarr; THDI <em>(%)</em></font><br /><br /><u>Output settings parameters</u><br /><font color=\"#3366ff\">OUT_U</font> <font color=\"#808080\">&rarr; Tension <em>(V)</em></font><br /><font color=\"#3366ff\">OUT_UTOL</font> <font color=\"#808080\">&rarr; Tol&eacute;rance <em>(%)</em></font><br /><font color=\"#3366ff\">OUT_THDU</font> <font color=\"#808080\">&rarr; THDU <em>(%)</em></font><br /><font color=\"#3366ff\">OUT_UDC</font> <font color=\"#808080\">&rarr; Composante DC <em>(V)</em></font><br /><font color=\"#3366ff\">OUT_F</font> <font color=\"#808080\">&rarr; Frequence <em>(HZ)</em></font><br /><font color=\"#3366ff\">OUT_FTOL</font> <font color=\"#808080\">&rarr; Tolerance <em>(%)</em></font><br /><font color=\"#3366ff\">OUT_VA</font> <font color=\"#808080\">&rarr; Power <em>(VA)</em></font><br /><font color=\"#3366ff\">OUT_W</font> <font color=\"#808080\">&rarr; Power <em>(W)</em></font><br /><font color=\"#3366ff\">OUT_COSPHI</font> <font color=\"#808080\">&rarr; Factor <em>(%)</em></font><br /><br /><u>Battery/Charger settings parameters</u></p><p><em><u>Battery:</u></em><br /><font color=\"#3366ff\">BAT_U</font> <font color=\"#808080\">&rarr; U Batt <em>(V)</em></font><br /><font color=\"#3366ff\">BAT_U_MAX</font> <font color=\"#808080\">&rarr; U Maxi <em>(V)</em></font><br /><font color=\"#3366ff\">BAT_U_MIN</font> <font color=\"#808080\">&rarr; U Mini <em>(V)</em></font><br /><font color=\"#3366ff\">BAT_AH</font> <font color=\"#808080\">&rarr; Capacity <em>(AH)</em></font><br /><font color=\"#3366ff\">BAT_LIFE</font> <font color=\"#808080\">&rarr; Life <em>(year)</em></font><br /><font color=\"#3366ff\">BAT_BRANCH</font> <font color=\"#808080\">&rarr; Branche <em>(Nbr)</em></font><br /><font color=\"#3366ff\">BAT_C1</font> <font color=\"#808080\">&rarr; Batt coeficient 1</font><br /><font color=\"#3366ff\">BAT_C2</font> <font color=\"#808080\">&rarr; Batt coeficient 2</font><br /><font color=\"#3366ff\">BAT_C3</font> <font color=\"#808080\">&rarr; Batt coeficient 3</font><br /><font color=\"#3366ff\">BAT_C4</font> <font color=\"#808080\">&rarr; Batt coeficient 4</font><br /><br /><em><u>Charger:</u></em><br /><font color=\"#3366ff\">CHRG_U</font> <font color=\"#808080\">&rarr; U Floating <em>(V)</em></font><br /><font color=\"#3366ff\">CHRG_I</font> <font color=\"#808080\">&rarr; I charger <em>(A)</em></font><br /><font color=\"#3366ff\">CHRG_T&deg;C</font> <font color=\"#808080\">&rarr; Temperature <em>(&deg;C)</em></font><br /><br /><u>Miscellaneous:</u><br /><br /><em><u>Ate:</u></em><br /><font color=\"#3366ff\">ATE_REV</font> <font color=\"#808080\">&rarr; ATE revision</font><br /><font color=\"#3366ff\">ATE_HOST</font> <font color=\"#808080\">&rarr; ATE host name</font><br /><br /><em><u>Sequence:</u></em><br /><font color=\"#3366ff\">PLAY_SDC</font> <font color=\"#808080\">&rarr; Sequence in progress</font><br /><font color=\"#3366ff\">PLAY_SEQ</font> <font color=\"#808080\">&rarr; Step in progress</font><br /><font color=\"#3366ff\">PLAY_STEP</font> <fon