(96, 12, 'Recommendation to store the resources files', 4, '2010-08-27 15:49:48', '<p>Recommendation to store the resources files used by the test specification</p><p>This recommendation</p><p>&nbsp;- has a target to structure the resources files to increase the facility of usage</p><p>&nbsp;- is associated at the <a href=\"document_show.php?document_id=11\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Variable usage\">VARIABLE usage</a>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><u>Tree strategic variables:</u></p><p>&nbsp;- <font color=\"#3366ff\">SCAN_REF </font><font color=\"#808080\">&rarr; SKU Reference</font></p><p>&nbsp;- <font color=\"#3366ff\">GAME_NAME</font> <font color=\"#808080\">&rarr; Game name <em>(used for path)</em></font></p><p>&nbsp;- <font color=\"#3366ff\">CONTROL_NAME</font> <font color=\"#808080\">&rarr; Control name <em>(used for path)</em></font></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><u>Test specification usage:</u></p><p>&nbsp;S:\\<strong><font size=\"3\"><font color=\"#ff0000\">~</font></font></strong><strong><font color=\"#3366ff\">GAME_NAME</font><font size=\"3\"><font color=\"#ff0000\">~</font></font></strong>\\Bitmaps\\<strong><font color=\"#ff0000\"><font size=\"3\">~</font></font><font color=\"#3366ff\">CONTROL_NAME</font><font color=\"#ff0000\"><font size=\"3\">~</font></font></strong>\\Connexion\\<strong><font color=\"#ff0000\"><font size=\"3\">~</font></font><font color=\"#3366ff\">SCAN_REF</font><font color=\"#ff0000\"><font size=\"3\">~</font></font></strong>.jpg</p><p><em>&nbsp;Replaced for example as:</em></p><p>&nbsp;S:\\<strong><font color=\"#800000\">Network Power Solution</font></strong>\\Bitmaps\\<strong><font color=\"#800000\">UnitHypotFunctionalTest</font></strong>\\Connexion\\<strong><font color=\"#800000\">SUA1000XLI</font></strong>.jpg&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><u>Complements:</u></p><p>&nbsp;<strong>S:\\</strong> <font color=\"#808080\">&rarr; Mounted network drive <em>(letter <strong>\'S\'</strong> as <strong>S</strong>tamp)</em></font> </p><p><strong>&nbsp;\\Bitmaps\\</strong>&nbsp;<font color=\"#808080\">&rarr; Repertory to store the bitmaps <em>(Files name can be used to store other files)</em></font></p><p><strong>&nbsp;\\Connexion\\</strong>&nbsp;<font color=\"#808080\">&rarr; Repertory to store the bitmaps used to explain the UUT connexion <em>(in Files directory the \'CustomTest\' can be used to store the personalization files)</em></font></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><u>Example:</u></p><p>&nbsp;<img src=\"../images/custom/example/RessourceFileRecommendation.jpg\" alt=\"RessourceFileRecommendation.jpg\" width=\"441\" height=\"141\" /></p>', '', ''),
(97, 14, 'Identify the Instrument ID to load a plug-in', 4, '2010-09-07 11:22:44', '<p><font size=\"3\"><strong>Identify the Instrument ID to load a plug-in in the &quot;Station&quot;, &quot;Plug-in&quot;, &quot;Driver&quot; section</strong></font></p><p><font color=\"#800000\"><u>Used only for the MEASure plug-in linked to SCPI instruments</u></font>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><u>Example:</u></p><p>&nbsp;<img src=\"../images/custom/plug-in/VisaExemple.jpg\" alt=\"Driver example\" width=\"763\" height=\"117\" /></p><p>&nbsp;The answer at the VISA request &quot;*IDN?&quot; for the Yokogawwa WT230 is the string &quot;YOKOGAWA,<strong><font color=\"#3366ff\">253502</font></strong>,0,F1.51&quot;</p><p>&nbsp;To identify the instrument at the initialization, the &quot;*IDN?&quot; is used and permit to find into the string an identifier like &quot;<strong><font color=\"#3366ff\">253502</font></strong>&quot; corresponding at the reference number of instrument</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><u>To define:</u></p><p>&nbsp;Open the VISA Interactive Control program and double click on the desired instrument</p><p>&nbsp;<img src=\"../images/custom/plug-in/VisaInterractiveCtrl.jpg\" alt=\"VISA interractive control\" width=\"391\" height=\"394\" /></p><p>&nbsp;Select the tab ViWrite and click Execute to send the command &quot;*IDN?\\n&quot;</p><p>&nbsp;<img src=\"../images/custom/plug-in/VisaViWrite.jpg\" alt=\"VisaViWrite\" width=\"570\" height=\"344\" /></p><p>&nbsp;Select the tab ViRead&nbsp;and click Execute to read the instrument answer&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;<img src=\"../images/custom/plug-in/VisaViRead.jpg\" alt=\"VisaViRead\" width=\"570\" height=\"344\" /></p><p>&nbsp;Chose in the answer the information that you want compare during the initialization</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><u>List of instrument identifier:</u>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;<strong>DMM</strong></p><p>&nbsp;</p><blockquote>HP 34970A &rarr; <font color=\"#3366ff\">34970A</font></blockquote><blockquote>HP 34401A&nbsp;&rarr; <font color=\"#3366ff\">34401A</font></blockquote><p>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;<strong>Power meter</strong></p><p>&nbsp;</p><blockquote>&nbsp;Yokogawa WT230 &rarr; <font color=\"#3366ff\">253502</font></blockquote><p>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p>', '', ''),
