MP   settings (the label being linked to the product address where the data   will be written). </font></em></blockquote><blockquote><em><u>3.1. Status :</u></em></blockquote><blockquote> <blockquote><table border=\"0\"><tbody><tr><td align=\"left\" style=\"width: 80px; height: 24px\">Command :</td><td><font color=\"#800000\">UUT:COMM:READ:STATUS(</font><font color=\"#800000\"><font color=\"#0000ff\">PROTOCOL,</font></font><font color=\"#800000\"><font color=\"#0000ff\">LABEL</font></font><font color=\"#800000\">) <font color=\"#008080\">~(VAR)~</font></font></td></tr></tbody></table><p>&nbsp;</p><table border=\"0\" width=\"713\" height=\"29\"><tbody><tr><td valign=\"top\" style=\"width: 80px; height: 24px\">Explanation : <br /></td><td valign=\"top\" style=\"width: 40px\"><font color=\"#0000ff\">PROTOCO</font><font color=\"#0000ff\">L</font> </td><td valign=\"top\" style=\"width: 20px\"><font color=\"#808080\">&rarr;</font> <br /></td><td valign=\"top\" style=\"width: 500px\"><font color=\"#808080\">Protocol short name</font> </td></tr><tr><td>&nbsp;</td><td><font color=\"#0000ff\">LABEL</font></td><td><font color=\"#808080\">&rarr;</font> </td><td><font color=\"#808080\">Status label</font></td></tr><tr><td>&nbsp;</td><td><font color=\"#800000\"> <font color=\"#008080\">VAR</font></font></td><td><font color=\"#808080\">&rarr;</font></td><td><font color=\"#808080\">Variable in which the status will be stored </font></td></tr></tbody></table></blockquote></blockquote><blockquote><em><u>3.2. Value :</u></em></blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><table border=\"0\"><tbody><tr><td align=\"left\" style=\"width: 80px; height: 24px\">Command :</td><td><font color=\"#800000\">UUT:COMM:READ:VALUE</font><font color=\"#800000\">(</font><font color=\"#800000\"><font color=\"#0000ff\">PROTOCOL,</font></font><font color=\"#800000\"><font color=\"#0000ff\">LABEL</font></font><font color=\"#800000\">)</font><font color=\"#800000\"> </font><font color=\"#800000\"><font color=\"#0080