(120, 20, 'SCPI commands for the USB-2-Xplug-in (Stamp3PlugInUSB2X.vi)', 5, '2010-11-15 14:58:28', '<p><strong><u>SCPI commands for the MICROLINK plug-in (Stamp3PlugInMICROLINK.vi</u></strong>)</p><br /><p>&nbsp;<u><strong>1. Plug-in setting : </strong></u></p><blockquote><p>This section gives all the SCPI commands necessary to the serial port configuration. </p></blockquote><blockquote><p><em><u>1.1. Initialization :</u></em></p><blockquote><table border=\"0\"><tbody><tr><td align=\"left\" style=\"width: 80px; height: 24px\">Command :</td><td><font color=\"#800000\">USB-::0x----::0x----::--------::RAW:</font><font color=\"#0000ff\">50</font><font color=\"#0000ff\">0</font></td></tr></tbody></table><p>&nbsp;</p><table border=\"0\" width=\"713\" height=\"98\"><tbody><tr><td style=\"height: 24px; width: 80px\">&nbsp;Explanation : </td><td style=\"width: 40px\"><font color=\"#800000\">USB...</font></td><td style=\"width: 20px\"><font color=\"#808080\">&rarr;</font></td><td style=\"width: 500px\"><font color=\"#808080\">Visa ressource name</font><font color=\"#808080\">, as defined in VISA Interactive Control</font><font color=\"#808080\"> </font><font color=\"#808080\">(*)</font><font color=\"#808080\">.<br /></font></td></tr><tr><td valign=\"top\">&nbsp;</td><td valign=\"top\"><font color=\"#0000ff\">500</font></td><td valign=\"top\"><font color=\"#808080\">&rarr;</font></td><td valign=\"top\"><font color=\"#808080\">CAN bit rate (kBits/s) (</font><font color=\"#808080\">0 : &quot;CAN disabled&quot;,&nbsp; 10 : &quot;10 kBits/s&quot;,&nbsp;</font><font color=\"#808080\"> 20 : &quot;20 kBits/s&quot;</font><font color=\"#808080\">,</font><font color=\"#808080\"> 50 : &quot;50 kBits/s&quot;</font><font color=\"#808080\">,</font><font color=\"#808080\"> 100 : &quot;100 kBits/s&quot;</font><font color=\"#808080\">,</font><font color=\"#808080\"> 125 : &quot;125 kBits/s&quot;</font><font color=\"#808080\">,</font><font color=\"#808080\"> 250 : &quot;250 kBits/s&quot;</font><font color=\"#808080\">,</font><font color=\"#808080\"> 500 : &quot;500 kBits/s&quot;</font><font color=\"#808080\">,</font><font color=\"#808080\"> 800 : &quot;800 kBits/s&quot;</font><font color=\"#808080\">,</font><font color=\"#808080\"> 1000 : &quot;1000 kBits/s&quot;</font><font color=\"#808080\">)</font></td></tr></tbody></table></blockquote><p><font color=\"#808080\">(*) : See <a href=\"http://zone.ni.com/devzone/cda/tut/p/id/4478#toc1\">National Instruments\' webpage</a> for more informations.</font></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><em><u>1.2. Change CAN bus settings :</u></em> </p><blockquote><table border=\"0\"><tbody><tr><td align=\"left\" style=\"width: 80px; height: 24px\">Command :</td><td><font color=\"#800000\">UUT:COMM:PARAM:SET(</font><font color=\"#0000ff\">50</font><font color=\"#0000ff\">0</font><font color=\"#800000\">)</font></td></tr></tbody></table><p>&nbsp;</p><table border=\"0\" width=\"713\" height=\"70\"><tbody><tr><td valign=\"top\" style=\"width: 80px; height: 24px\">Explanation : <br /></td><td valign=\"top\" style=\"width: 40px\"><font color=\"#0000ff\">500</font> </td><td valign=\"top\" style=\"width: 20px\"><font color=\"#808080\">&rarr;</font> <br /></td><td valign=\"top\" style=\"width: 500px\"><font color=\"#808080\">CAN bit rate (kBits/s) (</font><font color=\"#808080\">0 : &quot;CAN disabled&quot;,&nbsp; 10 : &quot;10 kBits/s&quot;,&nbsp;</font><font color=\"#808080\"> 20 : &quot;20 kBits/s&quot;</font><font color=\"#808080\">,</font><font color=\"#808080\"> 50 : &quot;50 kBits/s&quot;</font><font color=\"#808080\">,</font><font color=\"#808080\"> 100 : &quot;100 kBits/s&quot;</font><font color=\"#808080\">,</font><font color=\"#808080\"> 125 : &quot;125 kBits/s&quot;</font><font color=\"#808080\">,</font><font color=\"#808080\"> 250 : &quot;250 kBits/s&quot;</font><font color=\"#808080\">,</font><font color=\"#808080\"> 500 : &quot;500 kBits/s&quot;</font><font color=\"#808080\">,</font><font color=\"#808080\"> 800 : &quot;800 kBits/s&quot;</font><font color=\"#808080\">,</font><font color=\"#808080\"> 1000 : &quot;1000 kBits/s&quot;</font><font color=\"#808080\">)</font> </td></tr></tbody></table></blockquote> <p><em><u>1.2. Synchronize </u></em><em><u>CAN bus communication :</u></em> </p><blockquote><table border=\"0\"><tbody><tr><td align=\"left\" style=\"width: 80px; height: 24px\">Command :</td><td><font color=\"#800000\">UUT:COMM:PARAM:SYNC(<font color=\"#0000ff\">0</font></font><font color=\"#0000ff\">,CR</font><font color=\"#0000ff\">,1</font><font color=\"#0000ff\">,1</font><font color=\"#0000ff\">0</font><font color=\"#800000\">)</font></td></tr></tbody></table><p>&nbsp;</p><table border=\"0\" width=\"713\" height=\"70\"><tbody><tr><td valign=\"top\" style=\"width: 80px; height: 24px\">Explanation : <br /></td><td valign=\"top\" style=\"width: 40px\"><font color=\"#0000ff\">1</font><br /></td><td valign=\"top\" style=\"width: 20px\"><font color=\"#808080\">&rarr;</font> <br /></td><td valign=\"top\" style=\"width: 500px\"><font color=\"#808080\">Timeout (ms)</font> </td></tr><tr><td valign=\"top\" style=\"height: 24px\">&nbsp;</td><td valign=\"top\"><font color=\"#0000ff\">10</font></td><td valign=\"top\"><font color=\"#808080\">&rarr;</font></td><td valign=\"top\" style=\"width: 537px\"><font color=\"#808080\">Rate (ms)</font></td></tr></tbody></table></blockquote> <p><em><u>1.4. Open CAN bus communication :</u></em> </p> </blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><table border=\"0\"><tbody><tr><td align=\"left\" style=\"width: 80px; height: 24px\">Command :</td><td><font color=\"#800000\">UUT:COMM:PARAM:OPEN()</font></td></tr></tbody></table></blockquote><blockquote><em><font color=\"#999999\">Note : The microlink authentication is done at this step, which explains the fact that thi step is relatively long.</font></em></blockquote><p><em><u>1.5. Close </u></em><em><u>CAN bus communication :</u></em></p></blockquote>  <blockquote><blockquote><table border=\"0\"><tbody><tr><td align=\"left\" style=\"width: 80px; height: 24px\">Command :</td><td><font color=\"#800000\">UUT:COMM:PARAM:CLOSE()</font></td></tr></tbody></table></blockquote></blockquote><p>&nbsp;<u><strong>2</strong><strong>. Send data :</strong></u></p><blockquote>This section gives all the available SCPI commands to send data to the unit under test via the serial port.&nbsp; <br /></blockquote><blockquote><em><font color=\"#999999\">Note : For each data type (order, parameter, string, file), the &quot;</font><font color=\"#800000\"><font color=\"#0000ff\">LABEL</font></font><font color=\"#999999\">&quot;   parameter refers to the definition of the data, made in the STAMP   settings (the label being linked to the product address where the data   will be written). </font></em></blockquote><blockquote><em><u>2.1. Order :</u></em></blockquote><blockquote> <blockquote><table border=\"0\"><tbody><tr><td align=\"left\" style=\"width: 80px; height: 24px\">Command :</td><td><font color=\"#800000\">UUT:COMM:SEND:ORDER(<font color=\"#0000ff\">PROTOCOL,LABEL</font></font><font color=\"#800000\"><font color=\"#0000ff\">,VALUE</font></font><font color=\"#800000\">)</font></td></tr></tbody></table><p>&nbsp;</p><table border=\"0\" width=\"713\" height=\"29\"><tbody><tr><td valign=\"top\" style=\"width: 80px; height: 24px\">Explanation : <br /></td><td valign=\"top\" style=\"width: 40px\"><font color=\"#800000\"><font color=\"#0000ff\">PROTOCOL</font></font> </td><td valign=\"top\" style=\"width: 20px\"><font color=\"#808080\">&rarr;</font> <br /></td><td valign=\"top\" style=\"width: 500px\"><font color=\"#808080\">Protocol short name</font> </td></tr><tr><td>&nbsp;</td><td><font color=\"#0000ff\">LABEL</font></td><td><font color=\"#808080\">&rarr;</font> </td><td><font color=\"#808080\">Order label</font></td></tr><tr><td>&nbsp;</td><td><font color=\"#0000ff\">VALUE</font></td><td><font color=\"#808080\">&rarr;</font></td><td><font color=\"#808080\">Order value (hexadecimal)</font></td></tr></tbody></table></blockquote> </blockquote><blockquote><em><u>2.2. Parameter :</u></em></blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><table border=\"0\"><tbody><tr><td align=\"left\" style=\"width: 80px; height: 24px\">Command :</td><td><font color=\"#800000\">UUT:COMM:SEND:</font><font color=\"#800000\">PARAM</font><font color=\"#800000\">(</font><font color=\"#800000\"><font color=\"#0000ff\">PROTOCOL,</font></font><font color=\"#800000\"><font color=\"#0000ff\">LABEL,VALUE</font></font><font color=\"#800000\">)</font></td></tr></tbody></table><p>&nbsp;</p><table border=\"0\" width=\"713\" height=\"29\"><tbody><tr><td valign=\"top\" style=\"width: 80px; height: 24px\">Explanation : <br /></td><td valign=\"top\" style=\"width: 40px\"><font color=\"#800000\"><font color=\"#0000ff\">PROTOCOL</font></font> </td><td valign=\"top\" style=\"width: 20px\"><font color=\"#808080\">&rarr;</font> <br /></td><td valign=\"top\" style=\"width: 500px\"><font color=\"#808080\">Protocol short name</font></td></tr><tr><td>&nbsp;</td><td><font color=\"#800000\"><font color=\"#0000ff\">LABEL</font></font></td><td><font color=\"#808080\">&rarr;</font> </td><td><font color=\"#808080\">Parameter label<br /></font></td></tr><tr><td>&nbsp;</td><td><font color=\"#0000ff\">VALUE</font></td><td><font color=\"#808080\">&rarr;</font> </td><td><font color=\"#808080\">Parameter value (decimal)<br /></font></td></tr></tbody></table></blockquote> </blockquote><blockquote><em><u>2.3. String :</u></em></blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><table border=\"0\"><tbody><tr><td align=\"left\" style=\"width: 80px; height: 24px\">Command :</td><td><font color=\"#800000\">UUT:COMM:SEND:STRING</font><font color=\"#800000\">(</font><font color=\"#800000\"><font color=\"#0000ff\">PROTOCOL,</font></font><font color=\"#800000\"><font color=\"#0000ff\">LABEL,STRING</font></font><font color=\"#800000\">)</font></td></tr></tbody></table><p>&nbsp;</p><table border=\"0\" width=\"713\" height=\"29\"><tbody><tr><td valign=\"top\" style=\"width: 80px; height: 24px\">Explanation : <br /></td><td valign=\"top\" style=\"width: 40px\"><font color=\"#800000\"><font color=\"#0000ff\">PROTOCOL</font></font> </td><td valign=\"top\" style=\"width: 20px\"><font color=\"#808080\">&rarr;</font> <br /></td><td valign=\"top\" style=\"width: 500px\"><font color=\"#808080\">Protocol short name</font> </td></tr><tr><td>&nbsp;</td><td><font color=\"#0000ff\">LABEL</font></td><td><font color=\"#808080\">&rarr;</font></td><td><font color=\"#808080\">String label</font></td></tr><tr><td>&nbsp;</td><td><font color=\"#0000ff\">STRING</font></td><td><font color=\"#808080\">&rarr;</font> </td><td><font color=\"#808080\">String value (no quotes)<br /></font></td></tr></tbody></table></blockquote> </blockquote><blockquote><em><u>2.4. File :</u></em></blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><table border=\"0\"><tbody><tr><td align=\"left\" style=\"width: 80px; height: 24px\">Command :</td><td><font color=\"#800000\">UUT:COMM:SEND:FILE</font><font color=\"#800000\">(</font><font color=\"#800000\"><font color=\"#0000ff\">PROTOCOL,</font></font><font color=\"#800000\"><font color=\"#0000ff\">LABEL,PATH</font></font><font color=\"#800000\">)</font></td></tr></tbody></table><p>&nbsp;</p><table border=\"0\" width=\"713\" height=\"29\"><tbody><tr><td valign=\"top\" style=\"width: 80px; height: 24px\">Explanation : <br /></td><td valign=\"top\" style=\"width: 40px\"><font color=\"#0000ff\">PROTOCOL</font> </td><td valign=\"top\" style=\"width: 20px\"><font color=\"#808080\">&rarr;</font> <br /></td><td valign=\"top\" style=\"width: 500px\"><font color=\"#808080\">Protocol short name</font> </td></tr><tr><td>&nbsp;</td><td><font color=\"#0000ff\">LABEL</font></td><td><font color=\"#808080\">&rarr;</font> </td><td><font color=\"#808080\">File label</font></td></tr><tr><td>&nbsp;</td><td><font color=\"#0000ff\">PATH</font></td><td><font color=\"#808080\">&rarr;</font> </td><td><font color=\"#808080\">File path (**)<br /></font></td></tr></tbody></ta