id\">&nbsp;</td><td class=\"mceVisualAid\"><font color=\"#800000\"> <font color=\"#008080\">VAR</font></font></td><td class=\"mceVisualAid\"><font color=\"#808080\">→</font> </td><td class=\"mceVisualAid\"><font color=\"#808080\">Variable in which the value will be stored </font></td></tr></tbody></table></blockquote> </blockquote><blockquote><i><u>3.3. String :</u></i></blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><table class=\"mceVisualAid\" border=\"0\"><tbody><tr><td class=\"mceVisualAid\" style=\"width: 80px; height: 24px;\" align=\"left\">Command :</td><td class=\"mceVisualAid\"><font color=\"#800000\">UUT:COMM:READ:STRING</font><font color=\"#800000\">(</font><font color=\"#800000\"><font color=\"#0000ff\">PROTOCOL,</font></font><font color=\"#800000\"><font color=\"#0000ff\">LABEL</font></font><font color=\"#800000\">)</font><font color=\"#800000\"> </font><font color=\"#800000\"><font color=\"#008080\">~(VAR)~</font></font></td></tr></tbody></table><p>&nbsp;</p><table class=\"mceVisualAid\" border=\"0\" width=\"713\" height=\"29\"><tbody><tr><td class=\"mceVisualAid\" style=\"width: 80px; height: 24px;\" valign=\"top\">Explanation : <br></td><td class=\"mceVisualAid\" style=\"width: 40px;\" valign=\"top\"><font color=\"#0000ff\">PROTOCO</font><font color=\"#0000ff\">L</font> </td><td class=\"mceVisualAid\" style=\"width: 20px;\" valign=\"top\"><font color=\"#808080\">→</font> <br></td><td class=\"mceVisualAid\" style=\"width: 500px;\" valign=\"top\"><font color=\"#808080\">Protocol short name</font> </td></tr><tr><td class=\"mceVisualAid\">&nbsp;</td><td class=\"mceVisualAid\"><font color=\"#0000ff\">LABEL</font></td><td class=\"mceVisualAid\"><font color=\"#808080\">→</font></td><td class=\"mceVisualAid\"><font color=\"#808080\">String label</font></td></tr><tr><td class=\"mceVisualAid\">&nbsp;</td><td class=\"mceVisualAid\"><font color=\"#800000\"> <font color=\"#008080\">VAR</font></font><br></td><td class=\"mceVisualAid\"><font color=\"#808080\">→</font> </td><t