OTOCOL,</font></font><font color=\"#800000\"><font color=\"#0000ff\">LABEL</font></font><font color=\"#800000\"><font color=\"#0000ff\">,VALUE,TIME,LOOP</font></font><font color=\"#800000\">) </font><font color=\"#800000\"><font color=\"#008080\">~(VAR)~</font></font></td></tr></tbody></table><p>&nbsp;</p><table class=\"mceVisualAid\" border=\"0\" width=\"713\" height=\"29\"><tbody><tr><td class=\"mceVisualAid\" style=\"width: 80px; height: 24px;\" valign=\"top\">Explanation : <br></td><td class=\"mceVisualAid\" style=\"width: 40px;\" valign=\"top\"><font color=\"#0000ff\">PROTOCO</font><font color=\"#0000ff\">L</font> </td><td class=\"mceVisualAid\" style=\"width: 20px;\" valign=\"top\"><font color=\"#808080\">→</font> <br></td><td class=\"mceVisualAid\" style=\"width: 500px;\" valign=\"top\"><font color=\"#808080\">Protocol short name</font> </td></tr><tr><td class=\"mceVisualAid\">&nbsp;</td><td class=\"mceVisualAid\"><font color=\"#0000ff\">LABEL</font> </td><td class=\"mceVisualAid\"><font color=\"#808080\">→</font> </td><td class=\"mceVisualAid\"><font color=\"#808080\">Value label</font></td></tr><tr><td class=\"mceVisualAid\">&nbsp;</td><td class=\"mceVisualAid\"><font color=\"#800000\"><font color=\"#0000ff\">VALUE</font></font></td><td class=\"mceVisualAid\"><font color=\"#808080\">→</font></td><td class=\"mceVisualAid\"><font color=\"#808080\">Expected value</font><font color=\"#808080\"> (decimal)</font></td></tr><tr><td class=\"mceVisualAid\">&nbsp;</td><td class=\"mceVisualAid\"><font color=\"#800000\"><font color=\"#0000ff\">TIME</font></font></td><td class=\"mceVisualAid\"><font color=\"#808080\">→</font></td><td class=\"mceVisualAid\"><font color=\"#808080\">Maximum time before end of check</font></td></tr><tr><td class=\"mceVisualAid\">&nbsp;</td><td class=\"mceVisualAid\"><font color=\"#800000\"><font color=\"#0000ff\">LOOP</font></font></td><td class=\"mceVisualAid\"><font color=\"#808080\">→</font></td><td class=\"mceVisualAid\"><font color=\"#808080\">Maximum number of check attempts</font></td></tr><tr><td class=\"mceVisualAid\">&nbsp;</td><td class=\"mceVisualAid\"><font color=\"#800000\"> <font color=\"#008080\">VAR<br></font></font></td><td class=\"mceVisualAid\"><font color=\"#808080\">→</font> </td><td class=\"mceVisualAid\"><font color=\"#808080\">Variable in which the value will be stored </font></td></tr></tbody></table></blockquote> </blockquote><blockquote><i><u>4.3. String :</u></i></blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><table class=\"mceVisualAid\" border=\"0\"><tbody><tr><td class=\"mceVisualAid\" style=\"width: 80px; height: 24px;\" align=\"left\">Command :</td><td class=\"mceVisualAid\"><font color=\"#800000\">UUT:COMM:READ:WSTRING</font><font color=\"#800000\">(</font><font color=\"#800000\"><font color=\"#0000ff\">PROTOCOL,</font></font><font color=\"#800000\"><font color=\"#0000ff\">LABEL</font></font><font color=\"#800000\"><font color=\"#0000ff\">,STRING,TIME,LOOP</font></font><font color=\"#800000\">) </font><font color=\"#800000\"><font color=\"#008080\">~(VAR)~</font></font></td></tr></tbody></table><p>&nbsp;</p><table class=\"mceVisualAid\" border=\"0\" width=\"713\" height=\"29\"><tbody><tr><td class=\"mceVisualAid\" style=\"width: 80px; height: 24px;\" valign=\"top\">Explanation : <br></td><td class=\"mceVisualAid\" style=\"width: 40px;\" valign=\"top\"><font color=\"#0000ff\">PROTOCO</font><font color=\"#0000ff\">L</font> </td><td class=\"mceVisualAid\" style=\"width: 20px;\" valign=\"top\"><font color=\"#808080\">→</font> <br></td><td class=\"mceVisualAid\" style=\"width: 500px;\" valign=\"top\"><font color=\"#808080\">Protocol short name</font> </td></tr><tr><td class=\"mceVisualAid\">&nbsp;</td><td class=\"mceVisualAid\"><font color=\"#0000ff\">LABEL</font> </td><td class=\"mceVisualAid\"><font color=\"#808080\">→</font> </td><td class=\"mceVisualAid\"><font color=\"#808080\">String label</font></td></tr><tr><td class=\"mceVisualAid\">&nbsp;</td><td class=\"mceVisualAid\"><font color=\"#800000\"><font color=\"#0000ff\">STRING</font></font></td><td class=\"mceVisualAid\"><font color=\"#808080\">→</font></td><td class=\"mceVisualAid\"><font color=\"#808080\">Expected string value<br></font></td></tr><tr><td class=\"mceVisualAid\">&nbsp;</td><td class=\"mceVisualAid\"><font color=\"#800000\"><font color=\"#0000ff\">TIME</font></font></td><td class=\"mceVisualAid\"><font color=\"#808080\">→</font></td><td class=\"mceVisualAid\"><font color=\"#808080\">Maximum time before end of check</font></td></tr><tr><td class=\"mceVisualAid\">&nbsp;</td><td class=\"mceVisualAid\"><font color=\"#800000\"><font color=\"#0000ff\">LOOP</font></font></td><td class=\"mceVisualAid\"><font color=\"#808080\">→</font></td><td class=\"mceVisualAid\"><font color=\"#808080\">Maximum number of check attempts</font></td></tr><tr><td class=\"mceVisualAid\">&nbsp;</td><td class=\"mceVisualAid\"><font color=\"#800000\"> <font color=\"#008080\">VAR</font></font></td><td class=\"mceVisualAid\"><font color=\"#808080\">→</font> </td><td class=\"mceVisualAid\"><font color=\"#808080\">Variable in which the string will be stored </font></td></tr></tbody></table></blockquote> </blockquote><blockquote><i><u>4.4. File :</u></i></blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><table class=\"mceVisualAid\" border=\"0\"><tbody><tr><td class=\"mceVisualAid\" style=\"width: 80px; height: 24px;\" align=\"left\">Command :</td><td class=\"mceVisualAid\"><font color=\"#800000\">UUT:COMM:READ:CFILE</font><font color=\"#800000\">(</font><font color=\"#800000\"><font color=\"#0000ff\">PROTOCOL,</font></font><font color=\"#800000\"><font color=\"#0000ff\">LABEL,PATH</font></font><font color=\"#800000\">)</font></td></tr></tbody></table><p>&nbsp;</p><table class=\"mceVisualAid\" border=\"0\" width=\"713\" height=\"29\"><tbody><tr><td class=\"mceVisualAid\" style=\"width: 80px; height: 24px;\" valign=\"top\">Explanation : <br></td><td class=\"mceVisualAid\" style=\"width: 40px;\" valign=\"top\"><font color=\"#0000ff\">PROTOCO</font><font color=\"#0000ff\">L</font></td><td class=\"mceVisualAid\" style=\"width: 20px;\" valign=\"top\"><font color=\"#808080\">→</font> <br></td><td class=\"mceVisualAid\" style=\"width: 500px;\" valign=\"top\"><font color=\"#808080\">Protocol short name</font> </td></tr><tr><td class=\"mceVisualAid\">&nbsp;</td><td class=\"mceVisualAid\"><font color=\"#0000ff\">LABEL</font> </td><td class=\"mceVisualAid\"><font color=\"#808080\">→</font> </td><td class=\"mceVisualAid\"><font color=\"#808080\">File label</font></td></tr><tr><td class=\"mceVisualAid\">&nbsp;</td><td class=\"mceVisualAid\"><font color=\"#0000ff\">PATH</font></td><td class=\"mceVisualAid\"><font color=\"#808080\">→</font> </td><td class=\"mceVisualAid\"><font color=\"#808080\">Path of the file that contains the list of the parameters to read, and the expected values</font><br></td></tr></tbody></table></blockquote> </blockquote><p><b><u>5. File infos</u></b></p><blockquote><p>&nbsp;With the ASCII plugin, it\'s possible to read, send or check a list of values given in a file (whose path is given in the <font color=\"#800000\"><font color=\"#0000ff\">PATH</font></font> parameter).</p><p>The following example gives an overview of the informations that can be found in this kind of file : </p><p><font color=\"#999999\">[UUT_DESCRIPTION]<br>serial =UUT_SERIAL</font></p><p><font color=\"#999999\">reference = UUT_REF<br>date = MM/DD/YYYY<br>time = HH:MM:SS</font></p><p><font color=\"#999999\">path_template = path/to/the/template.ini</font></p><p><font color=\"#999999\"><br>[PARAMETERS]<br>post_delay = 0.5<br><br>[SETTINGS]<br>SET_U_UTIL = 230.0<br>SET_U_BATT = 100.0<br>etc.</font></p><p>The first section (<font color=\"#999999\">UUT_DESCRIPTION</font>) gives the global informations relative to the unit under test.</p><p>The second section (<font color=\"#999999\">PARAMETERS</font>) sets the plugin parameter.The \"<font color=\"#999999\">post_delay</font>\"   parameter sets the wait time (in seconds) when reading or sending   parameters. It must be adapted to the unit under test time response   (default value : 0.5 second). </p><p>The last section (<font color=\"#999999\">SETTINGS</font>) lists all the parameters that will be read, sent or check in the unit under test.</p></blockquote>', '', '');
INSERT INTO `document_history_table` (`document_history_id`, `document_id`, `subject`, `created_by`, `created_date`, `description`, `filename`, `filedata`) VALUES
(122, 20, 'SCPI commands for the USB-2-X plug-in (Stamp3PlugInUSB2X.vi)', 5, '2010-11-15 14:59:00', '<p><strong><u>SCPI commands for the USB-2-X plug-in (Stamp3PlugInUSB2X.vi</u></strong>)</p><br /><p>&nbsp;<u><strong>1. Plug-in setting : </strong></u></p><blockquote><p>This section gives all the SCPI commands necessary to the serial port configuration. </p></blockquote><blockquote><p><em><u>1.1. Initialization :</u></em></p><blockquote><table border=\"0\"><tbody><tr><td align=\"left\" style=\"width: 80px; height: 24px\">Command :</td><td><font color=\"#800000\">USB-::0x----::0x----::--------::RAW:</font><font color=\"#0000ff\">50</font><font color=\"#0000ff\">0</font></td></tr></tbody></table><p>&nbsp;</p><table border=\"0\" width=\"713\" height=\"98\"><tbody><tr><td style=\"height: 24px; width: 80px\">&nbsp;Explanation : </td><td style=\"width: 40px\"><font color=\"#800000\">USB...</font></td><td style=\"width: 20px\"><font color=\"#808080\">&rarr;</font></td><td style=\"width: 500px\"><font color=\"#808080\">Visa ressource name</font><font color=\"#808080\">, as defined in VISA Interactive Control</font><font color=\"#808080\"> </font><font color=\"#808080\">(*)</font><font color=\"#808080\">.<br /></font></td></tr><tr><td valign=\"top\">&nbsp;</td><td valign=\"top\"><font color=\"#0000ff\">500</font></td><td valign=\"top\"><font color=\"#808080\">&rarr;</font></td><td valign=\"top\"><font color=\"#808080\">CAN bit rate (kBits/s) (</font><font color=\"#808080\">0 : &quot;CAN disabled&quot;,&nbsp; 10 : &quot;10 kBits/s&quot;,&nbsp;</font><font color=\"#808080\"> 20 : &quot;20 kBits/s&quot;</font><font color=\"#808080\">,</font><font color=\"#808080\"> 50 : &quot;50 kBits/s&quot;</font><font color=\"#808080\">,</font><font color=\"#808080\"> 100 : &quot;100 kBits/s&quot;</font><font color=\"#808080\">,</font><font color=\"#808080\"> 125 : &quot;125 kBits/s&quot;</font><font color=\"#808080\">,</font><font color=\"#808080\"> 250 : &quot;250 kBits/s&quot;</font><font color=\"#808080\">,</font><font color=\"#808080\"> 500 : &quot;500 kBits/s&quot;</font><font color=\"#808080\">,</font><font color=\"#808080\"> 800 : &quot;800 kBits/s&quot;</font><font color=\"#808080\">,</font><font color=\"#808080\"> 1000 : &quot;1000 kBits/s&quot;</font><font color=\"#808080\">)</font></td></tr></tbody></table></blockquote><p><font color=\"#808080\">(*) : See <a href=\"http://zone.ni.com/devzone/cda/tut/p/id/4478#toc1\">National Instruments\' webpage</a> for more informations.</font></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><em><u>1.2. Change CAN bus settings :</u></em> </p><blockquote><table border=\"0\"><tbody><tr><td align=\"left\" style=\"width: 80px; height: 24px\">Command :</td><td><font color=\"#800000\">UUT:COMM:PARAM:SET(</font><font color=\"#0000ff\">50</font><font color=\"#0000ff\">0</font><font color=\"#800000\">)</font></td></tr></tbody></table><p>&nbsp;</p><table border=\"0\" width=\"713\" height=\"70\"><tbody><tr><td valign=\"top\" style=\"width: 80px; height: 24px\">Explanation : <br /></td><td valign=\"top\" style=\"width: 40px\"><font color=\"#0000ff\">500</font> </td><td valign=\"top\" style=\"width: 20px\"><font color=\"#808080\">&rarr;</font> <br /></td><td valign=\"top\" style=\"width: 500px\"><font color=\"#808080\">CAN bit rate (kBits/s) (</font><font color=\"#808080\">0 : &quot;CAN disabled&quot;,&nbsp; 10 : &quot;10 kBits/s&quot;,&nbsp;</font><font color=\"#808080\"> 20 : &quot;20 kBits/s&quot;</font><font color=\"#808080\">,</font><font color=\"#808080\"> 50 : &quot;50 kBits/s&quot;</font><font color=\"#808080\">,</font><font color=\"#808080\"> 100 : &quot;100 kBits/s&quot;</font><font color=\"#808080\">,</font><font color=\"#808080\"> 125 : &quot;125 kBits/s&quot;</font><font color=\"#808080\">,</font><font color=\"#808080\"> 250 : &quot;250 kBits/s&quot;</font><font color=\"#808080\">,</font><font color=\"#808080\"> 500 : &quot;500 kBits/s&quot;</font><font color=\"#808080\">,</font><font color=\"#808080\"> 800 : &quot;800 kBits/s&quot;</font><font color=\"#808080\">,</font><font color=\"#808080\"> 1000 : &quot;1000 kBits/s&quot;</font><font color=\"#808080\">)</font> </td></tr></tbody></table></blockquote> <p><em><u>1.2. Synchronize </u></em><em><u>CAN bus communication :</u></em> </p><blockquote><table border=\"0\"><tbody><tr><td align=\"left\" style=\"width: 80px; height: 24px\">Command :</td><td><font color=\"#800000\">UUT:COMM:PARAM:SYNC(<font color=\"#0000ff\">0</font></font><font color=\"#0000ff\">,CR</font><font color=\"#0000ff\">,1</font><font color=\"#0000ff\">,1</font><font color=\"#0000ff\">0</font><font color=\"#800000\">)</font></td></tr></tbody></table><p>&nbsp;</p><table border=\"0\" width=\"713\" height=\"70\"><tbody><tr><td valign=\"top\" style=\"width: 80px; height: 24px\">Explanation : <br /></td><td valign=\"top\" style=\"width: 40px\"><font color=\"#0000ff\">1</font><br /></td><td valign=\"top\" style=\"width: 20px\"><font color=\"#808080\">&rarr;</font> <br /></td><td valign=\"top\" style=\"width: 500px\"><font color=\"#808080\">Timeout (ms)</font> </td></tr><tr><td valign=\"top\" style=\"height: 24px\">&nbsp;</td><td valign=\"top\"><font color=\"#0000ff\">10</font></td><td valign=\"top\"><font color=\"#808080\">&rarr;</font></td><td valign=\"top\" style=\"width: 537px\"><font color=\"#808080\">Rate (ms)</font></td></tr></tbody></table></blockquote> <p><em><u>1.4. Open CAN bus communication :</u></em> </p> </blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><table border=\"0\"><tbody><tr><td align=\"left\" style=\"width: 80px; height: 24px\">Command :</td><td><font color=\"#800000\">UUT:COMM:PARAM:OPEN()</font></td></tr></tbody></table></blockquote><blockquote><em><font color=\"#999999\">Note : The microlink authentication is done at this step, which explains the fact that thi step is relatively long.</font></em></blockquote><p><em><u>1.5. Close </u></em><em><u>CAN bus communication :</u></em></p></blockquote>  <blockquote><blockquote><table border=\"0\"><tbody><tr><td align=\"left\" style=