<font color=\"#0000ff\">stamp3ate</font></td><td>&nbsp;<font color=\"#0000ff\">stamp3drv</font></td><td>&nbsp;<font color=\"#0000ff\">stamp3inst</font></td><td><font color=\"#0000ff\">stamp3uut</font></td><td>&nbsp;<font color=\"#0000ff\">stamp3qua</font></td></tr><tr><td>&nbsp;<strong>Description</strong></td><td>&nbsp;Stamp3</td><td>&nbsp;Ate database</td><td>&nbsp;Driver database</td><td>&nbsp;Instrument parameters</td><td>&nbsp;UUT database</td><td>&nbsp;Quality database</td></tr><tr><td>&nbsp;<strong>Server</strong></td><td>&nbsp;10.216.20.101</td><td>&nbsp;10.216.20.101</td><td>&nbsp;10.216.20.101</td><td>&nbsp;10.216.20.101</td><td>&nbsp;10.216.20.101</td><td>&nbsp;10.216.20.101</td></tr><tr><td><strong>&nbsp;Port <em>(if need)</em></strong></td><td>&nbsp;3306</td><td>&nbsp;3306</td><td>&nbsp;3306</td><td>&nbsp;3306</td><td>&nbsp;3306</td><td>&nbsp;3306</td></tr><tr><td><strong>&nbsp;User</strong></td><td>&nbsp;indus</td><td>&nbsp;indus</td><td>&nbsp;indus</td><td>&nbsp;indus</td><td>&nbsp;indus</td><td>&nbsp;indus</td></tr><tr><td>&nbsp;<strong>Password</strong></td><td>&nbsp;test</td><td>&nbsp;test</td><td>&nbsp;test</td><td>&nbsp;test</td><td>&nbsp;test</td><td>&nbsp;test</td></tr><tr><td><strong>&nbsp;Database <em>(select)</em></strong></td><td>&nbsp;stamp3</td><td>&nbsp;stamp3ate</td><td>&nbsp;stamp3drv</td><td>&nbsp;stamp3inst</td><td>&nbsp;stamp3uut</td><td>&nbsp;dicotrack</td></tr></tbody></table></p><p align=\"left\"><br /><u>Remark:</u><br />It&rsquo;s possible to use the \'<font color=\"#0000ff\">Test</font>\' button to check the access&nbsp;to the MySQL database</p><p>&nbsp;<u><strong><br />Next step :</strong></u></p><p><a href=\"document_show.php?document_id=22\">Install the VISA runtime<br /></a></p>', '', '');
INSERT INTO `document_history_table` (`document_history_id`, `document_id`, `subject`, `created_by`, `created_date`, `description`, `filename`, `filedata`) VALUES
(200, 4, '[STAMP SETUP - MANUAL MODE] 1st step - Connect the network drives \'Q\', \'S\' &amp; \'T\'', 5, '2010-11-25 09:36:39', '<p><strong><u>[STAMP SETUP - MANUAL MODE] 1st step - Connect the network&nbsp;drives&nbsp;&nbsp;\'Q\', \'S\' &amp; \'T\':</u></strong></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><strong><u>Usage:</u></strong></p><p>The \'<strong>Q</strong>\' <em>(as <strong>Q</strong>uasar)</em>, \'<strong>S</strong>\' <em>(as <strong>S</strong>tamp)</em> and \'<strong>T</strong>\' <em>(as <strong>T</strong>est)</em> letters are used to identify the network drives.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><strong><u>Setup:</u></strong></p>Run the installation program located on \'<font color=\"#0000ff\">T:\\stamp3setup\\01_CopyConnectNetworkDrives.bat</font>\'.<p>&nbsp;<u><strong><br />Next step :</strong></u></p><p><a href=\"document_show.php?document_id=5\">Install and Setup the ODBC Server</a></p><p>&nbsp;</p>', '', ''),
(201, 28, '[STAMP SETUP] 3rd step: Install Stamp 3 (manual mode)', 5, '2010-11-25 09:20:38', '<p><strong><u>[STAMP SETUP] 3rd step - Install Stamp 3 (manual mode)<br /></u></strong></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><strong><u>Process help:</u></strong></p><p><br />1. <a href=\"document_show.php?document_id=4\">Connect the network drives \'Q\', \'S\' &amp; \'T\'</a></p><p>2. <a href=\"document_show.php?document_id=5\">Install and Setup the ODBC Server</a></p><p>3. <a href=\"document_show.php?document_id=22\">Install the VISA runtime</a></p><p>4. <a href=\"document_show.php?document_id=23\">Install the Stamp3 application</a></p><p>5. <a href=\"document_show.php?document_id=24\">Copy the Plugin directory</a></p>', '', ''),
(202, 27, '[STAMP SETUP] 3rd step: Install Stamp 3 (automatic mode)', 5, '2010-11-25 09:00:59', '<p><strong><u>[STAMP SETUP] 3rd step - Install Stamp 3 (automatic mode)<br /></u></strong></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><strong><u>Process help:</u></strong></p><p>Download and execute&nbsp; the file <a href=\"T:/stamp3setup/00_InstallStamp3.bat\" title=\"ConnectNetworkDrives.bat\"></a><font color=\"#0000ff\"><a href=\"../doc/InstallStamp3.bat\" title=\"ConnectNetworkDrives.bat\">InstallStamp3.bat</a></font><font color=\"#0000ff\">.</font></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><u><strong>Remark:</strong></u></p><p>This setup program is a standard program. Use all standard answers.</p>', '', ''),
(203, 26, '[STAMP SETUP] 2nd step: Map The \'Q\', \'S\' and \'T\' network drives', 5, '2010-11-25 09:12:41', '<p><strong><u>[STAMP SETUP] 2nd step - Map the </u></strong><strong><u>\'Q\', \'S\' &amp; \'T\' </u></strong><strong><u>network&nbsp;drives </u></strong></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><strong><u>Opening remark:</u></strong></p><p>The \'<strong>Q</strong>\' <em>(as <strong>Q</strong>uasar)</em>, \'<strong>S</strong>\' <em>(as <strong>S</strong>tamp)</em> and \'<strong>T</strong>\' <em>(as <strong>T</strong>est)</em> letters are used to identify the network drives.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><u><strong>Process help:</strong></u></p><p>Download and execute the file <font color=\"#0000ff\"><a href=\"../doc/ConnectNetworkDrives.bat\" title=\"ConnectNetworkDrives.bat\">ConnectNetworkDrives.bat</a></font><font color=\"#000000\">. <br /></font></p><p>Once the file is executed, open the Windows Explorer and check that the three network drives have been successfully mapped<br />(click on each letter to check that you can access to the corresponding network drive).</p><p>&nbsp;<u><strong><br />Next step :</strong></u></p><p><a href=\"document_show.php?document_id=27\">Install Stamp 3 (automatic mode)</a> or <a href=\"document_show.php?document_id=28\">Install Stamp 3 (manual mode) </a></p><p>&nbsp;</p>', '', ''),
(204, 25, '[STAMP SETUP] 1st step: Check that the drive letters are available', 5, '2010-11-25 08:50:22', '<p><strong><u>[STAMP SETUP] 1st step - Check that the drive letters are available<br /></u></strong></p><p><br /><u><strong>Opening remark:</strong></u></p><p><br />The \'<strong>Q</strong>\' (as <u><strong>Q</strong></u>uasar), \'<strong>S</strong>\' (as <u><strong>S</strong></u>tamp) and \'<strong>T</strong>\' (as <u><strong>T</strong></u>est) drive letters are necessary to use Stamp 3.&nbsp; </p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><u><strong>Process help:</strong></u></p><p><u><strong><br /></strong></u>Open the Windows Explorer and check that the \'Q\', \'S\' and \'T\' drive letters are available.<br />If not, the given drive letters must be unmapped in order to use Stamp3.<u><strong><br /><br />Next step :</strong></u></p><p><a href=\"document_show.php?document_id=26\">Map The \'Q\', \'S\' and \'T\' network drives</a></p>', '', ''),
(205, 24, '[STAMP SETUP - MANUAL MODE] 5th step - Copy the Plugin directory', 5, '2010-11-25 09:39:08', '<p>[STAMP SETUP - MANUAL MODE]<strong><u> 5th step - Copy the Plugin directory<br /></u></strong></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><u>Setup:</u></p>Run the installation program located on \'<font color=\"#0000ff\">T:\\stamp3setup\\06_CopyPluginDirectory.bat</font>\'.', '', ''),
(206, 23, '[STAMP SETUP - MANUAL MODE] 4th step - Install the Stamp3 application', 5, '2010-11-25 09:39:14', '<p><u><strong>[STAMP SETUP - MANUAL MODE]</strong></u><strong> </strong><strong><u>4th step - Install the Stamp3 application<br /></u></strong></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><u>Setup:</u></p><p>Run the installation program located on \'<font color=\"#0000ff\">T:\\stamp3setup\\05_InstallSTAMP3.exe</font>\'.<br /><br /><u>Remarks:</u><br />This setup program is a standard program. Use all standard answers</p><p><u><strong><br />Next step:</strong></u></p><p><a href=\"document_show.php?document_id=24\">Copy Plugin directory</a> </p><p>&nbsp;</p>', '', ''),
(207, 22, '[STAMP SETUP - MANUAL MODE] 3rd step - Install the VISA runtime', 5, '2010-11-25 09:39:19', '<p><u><strong>[STAMP SETUP - MANUAL MODE]</strong></u><strong><u> 3rd step - Install the VISA runtime<br /></u></strong></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><u>Setup:</u></p><p>Run the installation program located on \'<font color=\"#0000ff\">T:\\stamp3setup\\04_InstallVISAruntime.exe</font>\'.<br /><br /><u>Remarks:</u><br />This setup program is a standard program. Use all standard answers</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><u><strong><br />Next step:</strong></u></p><p><a href=\"document_show.php?document_id=23\">Install STAMP3</a> </p>', '', ''),
