(28, 13, 4, '2010-09-07 11:30:14', '<p>Set Priority:Elevée, Status:<font color=red>Fixed and verified</font>, Assign To:<font color=red></font></p><p>Description:</p><p><p>Creation of generic plug-in usable for the MEASure SCPI instrument</p><p>Update of program and Wizard</p><p>New document created to explain how to fin the identifier &quot;Identify the Instrument ID to load a plug-in&quot;</p></p>', '', ''),
(29, 7, 4, '2010-09-13 15:31:05', '<p>Set Priority:Normal, Status:<font color=red>Under investigation</font>, Assign To:SID</p><p>Description:</p><p><p><strong><u>Analyze realized with CDS</u></strong></p><p>&nbsp; As synthesis: Used label including the WHERE, WHAT and HOW</p><p>&nbsp; One part of WHERE and WHAT is implicitness into the SCPI structure</p><p><strong><u>Implementation</u></strong><strong><u> realized</u></strong>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;The SCPI tree is corrected to facilitate this usage, see the <a href=\"../document/document_show.php?document_id=3\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"New SCPI tree\"><strong>NEW SCPI tree</strong></a></p><p>&nbsp;The new SCPI usages are implemented into the two Stamp3 web pages</p><p>&nbsp;&rarr; Product | Sequence</p><p>&nbsp;&rarr; Station | Plug-in&nbsp;</p><p><u><strong>Need to finalize</strong></u></p><p>&nbsp;Correct the Instrument Wizard for using this easiness</p><p>&nbsp;Create a document to explain the philosophy of the label name &nbsp;</p></p>', '', ''),
(30, 7, 4, '2010-09-15 16:51:45', '<p>Set Priority:Normal, Status:<font color=red>In process</font>, Assign To:SID</p><p>Description:</p><p><p><strong><u>Implementation Realized</u></strong></p><p>&nbsp;The <strong>Wizard</strong> is corrected and grow at <strong><font color=\"#ff0000\">Rev 1.1.0</font></strong></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><strong><u>Need to finalize</u></strong></p><p>&nbsp;Create a document to explain the philosophy of the label name&nbsp;</p></p>', '', ''),
